description:
Tanner is obviously a Sean Cody favorite, however he is also a favorite of Jasper’s. 

“I feel like I’ve won the lottery. I get to come here and fuck these guys, its fucking awesome.”
“Awe shucks! Whatever, I love all the attention!” Tanner chimed in.

These two hit it off pretty quickly and after heading downtown for some lunch and a quick workout, headed back to the studio to breed and seed Jasper.

“There is just something so fucking hot about knowing Tanner’s load was being pushed deep into my hole.” Jasper was clearly a happy camper.
title: Jasper & Tanner: Bareback
